text: Urs Fäh (born 15 April 1964) is a Swiss equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Switzerland Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
